    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly a bit sad to let this one go, but it's time for a new home! This car is in absolutely stunning, showroom-ready condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. I've babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and meticulously detailed. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. You really have to see it in person to appreciate how flawless it is. Drop me a message if you'd like to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
