      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this absolute gem. I\u2019ve taken such good care of this beauty that it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in mint condition, inside and out\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found. I'm so sad to let it go, but I know it's going to make its next owner incredibly happy. It's a total dream to drive and looks stunning in the driveway. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
