    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example boasts a pristine Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry utilizing Bilstein dampers. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with zero signs of oxidation or panel misalignment. Mechanically, the valve clearances have been shimmed to tight tolerances, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. A turn-key powerhouse for the discerning purist.",
